Make your resume personal


- resumemaker.online
- jobscan
- resumereworded
- thisresumedoesnotexists.com

- One page only
- Relevant Skills
- Personalized
- Online Link


Use a predesigned resume template
Make the resume fit on 1 page
Include words from job description
Include name of the company you are applying to
Does your first item on your resume reflect what they are looking for
Experience titles demonstrate value
Do you have an online link
Remove the word I
No buzzword describing how great you are
Are you using action words
Measure everything in terms of impact, don't just describe
Technical knowledge should include what they are looking for
Include only sections/items that are impressive: Experience, Projects, Education, Technical Skills
No typos or bad grammar


Don't have an experience?
- Github
- Website
- 1~2 Big Projects
- Blog

LinkedIn
- Update profile as often
- Get referrals
- Get endorsements and recommendations
- Contact someone at the company you are applying to


